{"tid":2348481,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲打生活係單親家庭？","createTime":"2020-12-31T17:10:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T08:17:09.000Z","uid":140706,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6016bc930d7b926ea2f171b94e295414f39a0da9","tid":2348481,"uid":140706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T17:10:01.000Z","msg":"大時大節覺得好寂寞<br />\n同家人關係唔好 無溝通 無交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無好熟既朋友 唔會出去玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇巴絲打都係生活係單親家庭<br />\n單親家庭毒撚性格既機會係咪特別大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n感受唔到有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30c5c781d2e9a6c8bf30424ec0a1758ffa7b23e7","tid":2348481,"uid":231089,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T17:13:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係呀<br />\n大時大節都會覺得孤獨嘅<br />\n但只要有一個屋企人或者有一個朋友你覺得好重要嘅話其實都可以堅持落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd0a78d86f4f1470f94a4baace463422d4cf60bb","tid":2348481,"uid":1747,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T17:14:56.000Z","msg":"絲？"},{"pid":"a0214c7d8bf59f09b8e125b5af4679002e6b5ebb","tid":2348481,"uid":22907,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T17:17:30.000Z","msg":"我單親+無朋友+窮+樣衰+矮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e937d2a3fa680d5f0a94f3fa5ec348c1897e6b77","tid":2348481,"uid":9392,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T17:18:20.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"2b819851903599c8fa27f519796a7aff3216b190","tid"